Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.crd.v1alpha4

Class UrlFrom

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.crd.v1alpha4.UrlFrom
public class UrlFrom extends Object
Represents a reference to read the URL from a different Kubernetes object.

This allows the Application CRD to dynamically read the URL from another resource such as a Service, ConfigMap, or any other Kubernetes object.
